lenders.occupation: Life Catalyst to Women beyond Fifity
lenders.loan_because:
I believe that by empowering individual women, we support positive change in the world. 
By creating relationship, we hold each other in love and humanity.
By providing financial stability, we underpin social and physical well-being and development. 
By creating community, we increase the stability of families, and provide for the safety and nurturing of children and the aged.
As I grow my business, I support Kiva in the same manner that others have supported me.
lenders.occupational_info:
Each of us contains a spark that inspired us in our innocence. I have seen that by purposefully reclaiming our girlhood dreams, we can ignite our world, on a personal and global level.

The third era of life for women is the time for them to take their gifts out into the world. I teach them to get real about what they want and when they want it, and to make it so!
